-The number's not assigned. Sir.


512
00:28:38.310 --> 00:28:39.300
謝謝你
Thanks, Ginger.


513
00:28:41.720 --> 00:28:42.880
地下電話
A bootleg.


514
00:28:51.930 --> 00:28:53.260
想開一點
Take it easy.


515
00:28:53.360 --> 00:28:54.890
時運不濟  史丹斯
Tough break, Stens.


516
00:28:55.030 --> 00:28:57.060
我們會想念你的
We're going to miss you.


517
00:28:57.200 --> 00:28:58.830
真是太不公平了  史丹斯
Raw deal, Stensland.


518
00:29:02.440 --> 00:29:04.000
打小報告的來了
Here comes the snitch.


519
00:29:15.320 --> 00:29:17.250
實在不好意思  長官
Sorry about that, Lieutenant.


520
00:29:34.000 --> 00:29:35.330
你少惹麻煩  巴德
Stay out of trouble, Bud.


521
00:29:38.340 --> 00:29:39.710
我還有幾小時才要去報到
I got a few hours.


522
00:29:39.810 --> 00:29:40.710
走  我請你喝一杯
I'll buy you a drink.


523
00:29:40.810 --> 00:29:42.610
下次吧  我現在趕著去約會
Rain check. I got a hot date.


524
00:29:44.780 --> 00:29:47.270
對方是誰?  你用什麼名義逮捕她的
Who is she and what did you arrest her for?


525
00:29:47.420 --> 00:29:48.970
這是秘密
It's confidential.


526
00:29:49.120 --> 00:29:52.450
就是經常和文生合作的  那個雜誌社的名字一樣
Like that magazine that Vincennes scams for.


527
00:29:52.550 --> 00:29:53.920
噓噓
Hush-Hush.


528
00:29:55.220 --> 00:29:56.560
我們過一兩天再見了
I'll see you later in the week.


529
00:29:57.660 --> 00:29:59.590
我們到時再去快活  我請客
We'll do the town, on me.


530
00:29:59.730 --> 00:30:02.600
是嗎?我還是帶著皮夾以防萬一
Yeah. I'll bring my wallet just in case.


531
00:30:07.200 --> 00:30:08.330
明天見了
-See you tomorrow.


532
00:30:08.470 --> 00:30:10.030
等一下
-Hold on!


533
00:30:10.170 --> 00:30:11.430
我跟你一起走
I'll walk down with you.


534
00:30:20.220 --> 00:30:23.880
小毛頭  他想做給誰看
Punk kid. Who is he trying to impress?


535
00:30:24.020 --> 00:30:25.150
對呀!我也在懷疑
Yeah, I wonder.


536
00:30:25.290 --> 00:30:27.150
不過他倒是官運亨通
Got himself a real career going.


537
00:30:31.790 --> 00:30:33.920
威廉警官請接無線電
Sergeant Williams, pick up, please.


538
00:30:35.430 --> 00:30:36.760
威廉警官
Sergeant Williams?


539
00:30:40.370 --> 00:30:42.890
兇殺組有沒有人在?
Is there anybody up there in Homicide?


540
00:30:44.170 --> 00:30:45.500
到底有沒有人在?
Anybody there?


541
00:30:47.980 --> 00:30:49.070
我是艾斯利警官
Lieutenant Exley.


542
00:30:49.210 --> 00:30:51.770
市中心發生兇殺案了
You've got a homicide downtown.


543
00:30:51.950 --> 00:30:53.380
在夜貓子咖啡廳
-The Nite Owl Coffee Shop.


544
00:30:53.480 --> 00:30:54.510
我知道了
-I got it.


545
00:31:07.600 --> 00:31:08.760
長官  至少死了一個人
At least one person's dead.


546
00:31:08.960 --> 00:31:10.400
我路過想進去喝一杯咖啡
I stopped for coffee.


547
00:31:10.530 --> 00:31:11.970
不許任何人從這個門出來
No one comes through the front door. Understand?


548
00:31:12.070 --> 00:31:14.040
- 明白嗎?  - 明白
- Understand? - Yes，sir


549
00:32:49.460 --> 00:32:52.020
在街道兩頭設立路障  絕對
I want barricades at both ends of the street. Make sure--


550
00:32:53.700 --> 00:32:56.190
電話是我接的  案子是我的
I took the call. It's my case.


551
00:32:56.340 --> 00:32:57.360
你不會想接這個案子的
You don't want it


552
00:32:57.510 --> 00:32:58.630
案子也不會是你的
and you can't have it.


553
00:32:58.770 --> 00:32:59.800
電話是我接的
I took the call.


554
00:32:59.940 --> 00:33:02.040
案子是我的
It's mine.


555
00:33:02.180 --> 00:33:03.740
我派你當副手好了
I'll make you my second-in-command.


556
00:33:03.880 --> 00:33:06.510
組長  請到這邊來一下  到那邊去
Captain, over here, please.


557
00:33:06.780 --> 00:33:08.480
任何人都不許進出
No body allowed inside.


558
00:33:10.320 --> 00:33:12.720
廚子曾開過槍
The cook drew a gun and set it off.


559
00:33:12.820 --> 00:33:14.410
其它人死在男廁所
The rest died in the men's room.


560
00:33:19.390 --> 00:33:24.530
長官  我們找到了十五發散彈鎗彈殼
Sir we got a total of 15 spent 12-gauge Remington shotgun shells.


561
00:33:24.530 --> 00:33:27.260
我猜兇手有三人  手持一次裝填五發的散彈鎗
I'm betting 3 men, 5-shot capacity pumps,


562
00:33:27.400 --> 00:33:28.560
子彈射完剛好十五發
all of them emptying once.


563
00:33:28.700 --> 00:33:31.640
對不起  長官  我們認出一名死者的身份了
Excuse me, we got an I.D. on one of the victims.


564
00:33:32.440 --> 00:33:34.140
是狄克·史丹斯蘭
It's Dick Stensland.


565
00:33:36.550 --> 00:33:39.240
我一開始以為她是麗泰·海華
At first, I thought she was Rita Hayworth.


566
00:33:39.380 --> 00:33:40.780
對  我也是
Yeah, me too.


567
00:33:50.490 --> 00:33:52.480
真是逃過牢獄之災的好方法
Hell of a way to avoid prison.


568
00:34:03.340 --> 00:34:05.140
發生什麼事了?
What happened?


569
00:34:05.240 --> 00:34:07.730
好像是有三個人搶劫咖啡廳
Appears 3 men held up a coffee shop.


570
00:34:07.880 --> 00:34:11.000
收銀員拿出了手槍所以兇手把他給殺了
The guy at the register pulled a.38, so they killed him.


571
00:34:11.180 --> 00:34:14.380
然後再把店裏的人殺個精光
Then they killed everyone else.


572
00:34:15.880 --> 00:34:18.820
長官  夜貓子那件命案可以認屍了
Lieutenant, we're ready with that Nite Owl I.D.


573
00:34:24.590 --> 00:34:26.990
她是你女兒嗎?
Is this your daughter?


574
00:34:27.100 --> 00:34:29.460
我不知道
I don't know.


575
00:34:29.560 --> 00:34:30.720
我們知道這很不容易
We know this is difficult.


576
00:34:30.870 --> 00:34:32.460
你慢慢來
Take your time.


577
00:34:34.000 --> 00:34:36.160
她好像是我的蘇珊
It seems like my Susan.


578
00:34:36.300 --> 00:34:39.500
可是我的蘇珊是金髮不是紅髮
But my Susan was a blonde, not a redhead.


579
00:34:39.640 --> 00:34:41.730
你上次見到她是什麼時候?
When was the last time you saw her?


580
00:34:41.880 --> 00:34:44.310
就是聖誕節之前
Just before Christmas.


581
00:34:44.450 --> 00:34:46.640
我們吵了一架  我不喜歡她的男友
We'd fought. I didn't like her boyfriend.


582
00:34:47.950 --> 00:34:48.970
雷佛太太
Mrs. Lefferts


583
00:34:49.120 --> 00:34:52.880
你女兒有沒有任何特別的記號
does your daughter have any distinguishing marks?


584
00:34:52.990 --> 00:34:55.720
你弄錯了  先生  我很好
You got the wrong idea, mister. I'm fine.


585
00:34:56.790 --> 00:35:00.320
她大腿旁邊有個胎記
She has a birthmark on her hip.


586
00:35:05.830 --> 00:35:10.200
是她沒錯  我的寶貝
It's her. My baby!


587
00:35:13.510 --> 00:35:14.980
節哀順變  雷佛太太
I'm sorry, Mrs. Lefferts.


588
00:35:16.580 --> 00:35:19.050
誰負責偵辦的?
Who's in charge of this investigation?


589
00:35:19.210 --> 00:35:21.340
史密斯組長以及我本人  怎麼了?
Captain Smith and myself. Why?


590
00:35:23.490 --> 00:35:24.880
"夜貓子大屠殺 "
"The Nite Owl Massacre."


591
00:35:24.990 --> 00:35:26.850
儘管口氣誇張了點
Hyperbole aside


592
00:35:26.960 --> 00:35:30.320
這樣的大案子卻非得迅速破案才行
this is a heinous crime that requires swift resolution.


593
00:35:31.630 --> 00:35:32.720
死了六個人
Six victims.


594
00:35:32.860 --> 00:35:35.350
其中一個還是我們自己人  狄克·史丹斯蘭
One of them, one of our own. Dick Stensland.


595
00:35:35.900 --> 00:35:38.020
他是夜貓子的常客
He was a Nite Owl regular,


596
00:35:38.170 --> 00:35:40.360
挑錯了時間  走錯了地方
in the wrong place at the wrong time.


597
00:35:40.500 --> 00:35:42.440
動機似乎是搶劫
Robbery is the likely motive.


598
00:35:42.540 --> 00:35:47.170
由櫃檯上的手套印  以及初步的監識結果看來
We have rubber glove smears on the register and forensics


599
00:35:47.310 --> 00:35:48.870
兇手的確是三個人沒錯
tend toward a trio of shooters.


600
00:35:49.010 --> 00:35:51.380
而且我們已經有了重要線索了
We do have one hot lead.


601
00:35:51.480 --> 00:35:54.010
有人看見三個黑人青少年
Three Negro juveniles


602
00:35:54.150 --> 00:35:57.350
在葛瑞菲斯公園拿著散彈鎗亂射
were seen discharging shotguns in Griffith Park.


603
00:35:57.490 --> 00:36:00.650
有位公園管理員認出他們  開著一部48至50年
A park ranger I.D.'d them as driving a 1948-1950 Mercury coupe


604
00:36:01.090 --> 00:36:03.520
的福特褐紅色雙門跑車
maroon in color.


605
00:36:03.630 --> 00:36:07.220
一小時前警員問到一位賣報的
An hour ago a canvassing crew found a news vendor


606
00:36:07.360 --> 00:36:09.560
他說在深夜一點的時候
who saw a maroon Merc coupe parked


607
00:36:09.700 --> 00:36:11.560
看見褐紅色水星雙門跑車停在夜貓子門口
by the Nite Owl at 1 a.m.


608
00:36:11.670 --> 00:36:16.370
監理處已經整理出  水星雙門車的車主記錄了
DMV has come up with a registration list of Merc coupes.


609
00:36:16.510 --> 00:36:21.880
二人一組每組查訪三位車主

610
00:36:21.980 --> 00:36:24.470
局內的偵訊工作由艾斯利負責
Interrogations will be led by Lt. Edmund Exley.


611
00:36:27.950 --> 00:36:29.470
別吵了
Enough on that!


612
00:36:32.620 --> 00:36:34.050
各位  去把兇手給我抓回來
Gentlemen, just go out and get them.


613
00:36:34.160 --> 00:36:37.150
動用所有必要的警力
Use all necessary force.


614
00:36:37.330 --> 00:36:40.020
這是洛杉磯市民的命令
The people of Los Angeles demand it.


615
00:36:40.160 --> 00:36:41.320
解散
Dismissed.


616
00:36:45.000 --> 00:36:46.560
直接懸賞他們的人頭不更乾脆
Why not just put a bounty on them?


617
00:36:54.380 --> 00:36:55.670
可以走了嗎  懷特?
-Ready to roll?


618
00:36:55.780 --> 00:36:57.400
你自己去就好了  我另外有事
-You take them, I got something to do.


619
00:36:57.550 --> 00:36:58.100
萬一正好就是那三個
What if one of these names--?


620
00:36:58.310 --> 00:37:01.370
找別人跟你去
Get somebody else.


621
00:37:02.080 --> 00:37:04.420
名單拿到了
I got our assignments, Big V.


622
00:37:04.520 --> 00:37:07.820
照這份名單找下去一輩子也找不到
We go by this list, we got zero chance of making this collar.


623
00:37:07.920 --> 00:37:09.950
我有位線人對傑佛遜街以南很熟
I got a guy who knows what happens south of Jefferson.


624
00:37:10.090 --> 00:37:11.420
他可以幫我們抓到人
He'll put us at 50-50.


625
00:37:11.530 --> 00:37:13.790
傑克  你幹什麼?
What are you doing?


626
00:37:13.800 --> 00:37:17.020
你上一次就是這樣子才惹上一身麻煩的
It's the same sort of thing that got you in trouble before.


627
00:37:17.070 --> 00:37:18.400
我就跟你冒這個險
I'll take those odds.


628
00:37:22.800 --> 00:37:23.830
現在開始由我們來
We got it from here.


629
00:37:26.410 --> 00:37:28.540
你們應該隨身帶著攝影記者的
You two should bring along a photographer.


630
00:37:33.880 --> 00:37:35.750
我想查一下你一位顧客的地址
I need an address on a customer of yours.


631
00:37:35.850 --> 00:37:37.040
她的名字叫琳恩
Her name is Lynn.


632
00:37:37.190 --> 00:37:38.480
你就丟給我這麼個名字?
-That's all I got to go on?


633
00:37:38.590 --> 00:37:39.520
對
-Yeah.


634
00:37:39.650 --> 00:37:42.590
你很清楚我是什麼人  所以上道一點吧!
You already know who I mean, so cough it up.


635
00:37:42.720 --> 00:37:45.220
上頭有收帳跟送貨的地址
There's a billing address and a delivery address.


636
00:38:12.520 --> 00:38:13.890
你是皮爾斯·巴卻嗎?
Are you Pierce Patchett?


637
00:38:15.260 --> 00:38:16.450
是
I am.


638
00:38:18.060 --> 00:38:20.720
你是來勸募警察福利基金的嗎?
Are you soliciting for police charities?


639
00:38:20.730 --> 00:38:22.890
上一次是你打電話來的吧?
Last time you called my office.


640
00:38:23.030 --> 00:38:25.760
到下面的車庫  我們到那兒談
Go on down to the driveway. We'll talk there.


641
00:38:37.110 --> 00:38:38.080
你有什麼事?
What can I do for you?


642
00:38:39.610 --> 00:38:41.050
你昨晚在哪裏?
-Where were you last night?


643
00:38:41.150 --> 00:38:43.120
在這裏舉行晚宴
-I was here hosting a party.


644
00:38:44.950 --> 00:38:46.550
把狄克·史丹斯蘭的事告訴我
Tell me about Dick Stensland.


645
00:38:46.690 --> 00:38:49.180
我不認識他  你是
I don't know him, Mr.--?


646
00:38:49.320 --> 00:38:50.660
懷特警員
Officer White.


647
00:38:51.790 --> 00:38:53.350
你認識蘇珊雷佛嗎?
You know Sue Lefferts?


648
00:38:53.500 --> 00:38:55.490
你知道我認識的  你看見我跟她在一起的
You know I do. You saw me with her.


649
00:38:57.500 --> 00:38:59.490
你怎麼找到我的?
How did you find me?


650
00:38:59.630 --> 00:39:00.970
尼克的烈酒商店
Nick's Liquor.


651
00:39:01.070 --> 00:39:04.230
是琳恩·佈雷肯寫的收帳地址
This is where Lynn Bracken's booze bills go.


652
00:39:04.370 --> 00:39:05.500
對哦!
Of course.


653
00:39:08.540 --> 00:39:11.210
蘇珊雷佛在夜貓子死了
Sue Lefferts died at the Nite Owl.


654
00:39:11.350 --> 00:39:12.810
我正在調查這件案子
I'm investigating.


655
00:39:15.180 --> 00:39:17.080
沒什麼事吧?  巴卻先生
Everything all right?


656
00:39:17.190 --> 00:39:18.910
沒事  謝謝你
Fine, Phillip, thank you.


657
00:39:23.260 --> 00:39:26.060
你另外那個保鏢巴茲呢?
What happened to the other guy, Buzz?


658
00:39:26.160 --> 00:39:28.290
巴茲·米克斯已經不替我工作了
Buzz Meeks no longer works for me.


659
00:39:28.460 --> 00:39:29.520
雷佛在聖誕夜似乎被打了
Lefferts looked beat-up Christmas Eve


660
00:39:29.660 --> 00:39:31.100
可是她卻沒報案  為什麼?
but didn't act it. Why?


661
00:39:31.200 --> 00:39:33.460
我想她是被網球拍打到的
I think she'd been hit in the face with a tennis racket.


662
00:39:33.570 --> 00:39:37.240
她很喜歡打雙打
She was a big doubles fan.


663
00:39:38.010 --> 00:39:40.600
你是命案死者的友人
You're a known associate of a woman killed in a mass murder.


664
00:39:41.880 --> 00:39:44.210
要不要到局裏去跟我們談?
-Want to go downtown to discuss this?


665
00:39:44.580 --> 00:39:46.770
只是為了這件事嗎  警察先生
-Is this official?


666
00:39:46.920 --> 00:39:51.040
我怎麼覺得你似乎是為了個人的私事來找我的
Somehow I have the feeling this is more personal with you.


667
00:39:54.820 --> 00:39:56.850
好了
All right, then


668
00:39:56.990 --> 00:40:01.160
你現在是奉命調查跟命案有關的事情嗎?
are you concerned about criminal matters peripheral to the murders?


669
00:40:01.300 --> 00:40:05.270
目前沒有  那你不見得要向上級報告羅?
-Not at the moment. -You're not obligated to report them?


670
00:40:07.500 --> 00:40:09.940
為什麼雷佛臉上會有淤血?
Why were Lefferts' eyes black?


671
00:40:10.040 --> 00:40:12.910
我需要一位麗泰·海華來充實我影棚的陣容
I needed a Rita Hayworth to fill out my little studio.


672
00:40:13.010 --> 00:40:14.170
什麼影棚?
What little studio?


673
00:40:14.310 --> 00:40:18.180
我們那兒有很多像電影明星的女孩
Well, there's Gardner, Russell, Monroe, Turner.


674
00:40:18.280 --> 00:40:20.870
琳恩是我的薇洛尼卡.雷克
Lynn Bracken is my Veronica Lake.


675
00:40:21.020 --> 00:40:23.510
我專找長的像電影明星的女孩
I use girls that look like movie stars.


676
00:40:23.650 --> 00:40:26.710
有時難免得稍微整容一下
Sometimes I employ a plastic surgeon.


677
00:40:26.860 --> 00:40:29.950
那晚正好被你看見了
When the work was done, that's when you saw us.


678
00:40:30.090 --> 00:40:31.920
所以她老母認不出她來
