01:15:22.320 --> 01:15:23.750
艾利斯也在  過來
Exley, over here.


1195
01:15:23.850 --> 01:15:25.680
笑一下  英奈茲
Smile, Inez.


1196
01:15:25.820 --> 01:15:28.810
他是你的大英雄吧
Is he your hero?


1197
01:15:28.960 --> 01:15:30.080
各位  這個標題怎麼樣?
Fellas, how about this?


1198
01:15:30.260 --> 01:15:32.920
"夜貓子案英雄推著被害人走出醫院 "
"Rape Victim Wheeled Out by Nite Owl Hero."


1199
01:15:39.170 --> 01:15:40.890
他們只得到了薇洛妮卡雷克
All they get is Veronica Lake.


1200
01:15:43.600 --> 01:15:45.630
而我得到琳恩瑪格莉特佈雷肯
I get Lynn Margaret Bracken.


1201
01:15:57.020 --> 01:15:58.240
比斯比
"Bisbee?"


1202
01:16:00.290 --> 01:16:01.620
我在那兒長大的
I grew up there.


1203
01:16:04.060 --> 01:16:06.390
我過幾年要回那兒去
I'm going back in a couple of years,


1204
01:16:06.530 --> 01:16:08.590
開一家服裝店
open up a dress shop.


1205
01:16:10.600 --> 01:16:13.530
比斯比的女孩需要好衣服打扮
The girls in Bisbee need a little glamour.


1206
01:16:19.240 --> 01:16:20.760
這疤是怎來的?
Where'd this come from?


1207
01:16:22.610 --> 01:16:25.040
我當年十二歲  我爸拿著酒瓶要砸我媽
I was 12. My dad went after my mother with a bottle.


1208
01:16:25.180 --> 01:16:26.410
我正好擋在中間
I got in the way.


1209
01:16:28.510 --> 01:16:29.740
所以是你救了你媽的?
So you saved her.


1210
01:16:31.580 --> 01:16:32.850
也救不了她多久
Not for long.


1211
01:16:36.020 --> 01:16:37.460
很對不起  這不關我的事的
-I'm sorry. It's none of my business.


1212
01:16:37.560 --> 01:16:39.990
他把我綁在暖氣機上面
-He tied me to the radiator.


1213
01:16:40.090 --> 01:16:43.080
我看著他用熨斗把我媽打死
I watched him beat my mother to death with a tire iron


1214
01:16:45.700 --> 01:16:47.360
然後他把我丟在那兒
and he left me there.


1215
01:16:49.770 --> 01:16:52.760
三天後學校督學才發現我們
Three days before a truant officer found us.


1216
01:16:55.840 --> 01:16:57.970
警方一直沒有找到我老頭
They never found the old man.


1217
01:17:07.090 --> 01:17:09.610
所以你才當警察的?
Is that why you became a cop?


1218
01:17:09.760 --> 01:17:11.650
為了討個公道?
To get even?


1219
01:17:12.890 --> 01:17:13.950
或許吧
Maybe.


1220
01:17:16.060 --> 01:17:17.530
你喜歡當警察嗎?
Do you like it?


1221
01:17:20.800 --> 01:17:21.990
以前喜歡
I used to.


1222
01:17:24.040 --> 01:17:27.340
如今這差事卻變成恃強凌弱了
Now it's all strong-arm, sitting duck stuff.


1223
01:17:27.970 --> 01:17:29.070
如果
If I could


1224
01:17:30.610 --> 01:17:33.340
如果我能有機會到兇殺組去
get a chance to work Homicide


1225
01:17:33.480 --> 01:17:35.410
像真正的刑警一樣辦案
like a real detective.


1226
01:17:36.720 --> 01:17:40.020
那個痞子艾斯利他殺錯人了
That prick, Exley, he shot the wrong guys.


1227
01:17:40.150 --> 01:17:41.710
殺死史丹斯蘭的人還逍遙法外
Whoever killed Stensland's still around.


1228
01:17:41.850 --> 01:17:44.520
我內心裏很清楚  我知道
I know it in here. I know it.


1229
01:17:45.460 --> 01:17:47.390
夜貓子那件案子不太對勁
Something's wrong with the Nite Owl.


1230
01:17:47.530 --> 01:17:49.260
只是我沒辦法證明而已
I just can't prove it, that's all.


1231
01:17:51.030 --> 01:17:52.620
我不夠聰明
I'm not smart enough.


1232
01:17:54.930 --> 01:17:57.900
我只是上頭長官用來嚇唬別人的工具而已
I'm just the guy they bring in to scare the other guy shitless.


1233
01:18:01.470 --> 01:18:02.630
你錯了
You're wrong.


1234
01:18:03.710 --> 01:18:06.540
你找到巴卻  你找到了我
You found Patchett. You found me.


1235
01:18:06.680 --> 01:18:08.480
你已經夠聰明了
You're smart enough.


1236
01:18:20.190 --> 01:18:22.660
巴德·懷特  什麼風把你吹到地下室來的?
Bud White! What brings you down to the basement?


1237
01:18:27.100 --> 01:18:29.000
我有幾個夜貓子案的問題想要問你
I got a couple of Nite Owl questions.


1238
01:18:29.100 --> 01:18:31.160
不知道你有沒有看過報紙
Don't know if you read the papers,


1239
01:18:31.170 --> 01:18:32.660
那個案子已經結了
but that case is closed.


1240
01:18:34.270 --> 01:18:36.710
你有沒有那裏覺得不對勁的
Anything bother you about it?


1241
01:18:36.840 --> 01:18:40.300
有  就是那些送貨的  還沒把這些東西給抬走
The fact that the pack-up boys haven't hauled this shit out of here yet.


1242
01:18:45.180 --> 01:18:49.280
我們查到嫌犯的三把散彈鎗彈道跟夜貓子的彈殼一致
The suspects' 3 shotguns match the strike marks on the shell casings.


1243
01:18:50.190 --> 01:18:52.520
你還要什麼證據?
What more do you want?


1244
01:19:04.000 --> 01:19:05.330
掛照片的牆上有血
There's blood on the wall here.


1245
01:19:06.570 --> 01:19:09.010
不是除了廚子以外的人  都是在男廁所被殺的嗎?
I thought everyone got shot in the men's room.


1246
01:19:09.110 --> 01:19:11.740
那是史丹斯蘭的血
That is Stensland's blood.


1247
01:19:11.880 --> 01:19:13.570
史丹斯?  對
Stensland? Yeah.


1248
01:19:13.710 --> 01:19:14.740
他頭上被狠狠挨了一記
Blow to the head.


1249
01:19:14.880 --> 01:19:17.350
兇手把他拖到男廁時他可能已經昏迷了
Probably unconscious when they dragged him in the john.


1250
01:19:19.220 --> 01:19:20.310
他們有沒有打其它的人?
Did they hit anyone else?


1251
01:19:20.490 --> 01:19:22.090
沒有  不過他是個警察
No, but he was a cop.


1252
01:19:22.100 --> 01:19:23.850
可能想要反抗吧
Probably tried to do something.


1253
01:19:27.790 --> 01:19:29.520
吉士三明治  黑咖啡
Grilled cheese, black coffee.


1254
01:19:29.660 --> 01:19:31.600
有人跟他坐在一起
Someone was sitting next to him.


1255
01:19:35.370 --> 01:19:37.170
有兩個被害人是女的  對吧

1256
01:19:37.300 --> 01:19:40.070
對  派蒂·杜魯卡  夜班女服務生
Yeah, Patti DeLuca, the night shift waitress,


1257
01:19:40.080 --> 01:19:41.700
還有一位叫做蘇珊·雷佛
and a Susan Lefferts.


1258
01:19:46.110 --> 01:19:47.600
蘇珊·雷佛?
Susan Lefferts.


1259
01:19:49.520 --> 01:19:50.610
對  怎麼樣?
Yeah, what about her?


1260
01:19:54.020 --> 01:19:55.950
不用客氣
You're welcome!


1261
01:19:57.790 --> 01:19:59.120
雷佛太太
Mrs. Lefferts


1262
01:20:01.590 --> 01:20:02.690
雷佛太太
Mrs. Lefferts?


1263
01:20:02.830 --> 01:20:05.460
我是洛杉磯警局的懷特警員
I'm Officer White, LAPD.


1264
01:20:07.900 --> 01:20:11.060
談談你那天在法院提到的你女兒的那位男友好嗎?
Tell me about the boyfriend you mentioned at the coroner's office.


1265
01:20:11.240 --> 01:20:14.210
我跟你們說過  我不喜歡她那個男朋友
I told you I didn't approve of that boyfriend.


1266
01:20:14.340 --> 01:20:16.270
他那麼老了跟你不配
He was too old for you.


1267
01:20:16.380 --> 01:20:18.470
你還讓他對我那麼兇
And you let him be fresh with me.


1268
01:20:20.480 --> 01:20:23.350
有一天我不在家的時候  他們到我家來
They came here one day when I wasn't home.


1269
01:20:23.420 --> 01:20:25.350
隔壁的簡森太太她說
Mrs. Jensen next door said


1270
01:20:25.480 --> 01:20:28.210
她看見蘇珊的男朋友跟另外一個男人在一起
she saw Susie's boyfriend and another man and


1271
01:20:28.590 --> 01:20:31.450
她還說她聽見一陣騷動
she heard a ruckus.


1272
01:20:31.820 --> 01:20:33.050
你女兒的男朋友叫什麼名字?
What was his name?


1273
01:20:33.190 --> 01:20:36.220
他根本就沒有跟我介紹
We weren't properly introduced.


1274
01:20:36.360 --> 01:20:38.890
蘇珊都叫他沐恩魯恩什麼的
Susie gave him a nickname, Muns or Luns.


1275
01:20:39.030 --> 01:20:40.430
史丹恩?
Stens?


1276
01:20:40.570 --> 01:20:41.620
是不是史丹恩?
Was it Stens?


1277
01:20:41.770 --> 01:20:43.000
或許是吧
Maybe.


1278
01:20:43.140 --> 01:20:44.160
我不知道
I don't know.


1279
01:20:44.300 --> 01:20:45.500
你看看照片
Look.


1280
01:20:49.010 --> 01:20:50.030
就是他
That's him.


1281
01:20:50.180 --> 01:20:51.970
就是他
That's him.


1282
01:20:56.980 --> 01:20:58.710
你說鄰居聽到騷動
You said a neighbor heard a ruckus.


1283
01:20:59.820 --> 01:21:02.380
是在外面嗎?還是裏面?
Was it outside? Inside?


1284
01:21:03.120 --> 01:21:04.380
在外面
Outside.


1285
01:21:04.520 --> 01:21:09.050
簡森太太說他們一直吵吵到房子下面去了
And then Mrs. Jensen said they kept going under the house.


1286
01:21:12.700 --> 01:21:15.490
你該走了  警察先生
You have to leave now, officer.


1287
01:21:16.370 --> 01:21:17.100
這兒過去是那裏?
-What's through here?


1288
01:21:17.240 --> 01:21:20.030
放雜物的房間
-Just a room full of old things.


1289
01:21:20.170 --> 01:21:21.400
不要動它
Don't move that!


1290
01:21:24.440 --> 01:21:25.240
不要理會那股種臭味了
Don't mind the smell.


1291
01:21:25.380 --> 01:21:27.640
大概是有老鼠死在牆後面了
I think a rat died behind the wall.


1292
01:21:29.420 --> 01:21:31.350
我的蘇珊是個好女孩
My Susie was a good girl.


1293
01:21:31.480 --> 01:21:34.150
她從來沒有惹過任何麻煩的
She was never in any kind of trouble at all!


1294
01:22:45.930 --> 01:22:48.190
李蘭·米克斯? 沒聽過
"Leland Meeks." Never heard of you.


1295
01:22:48.330 --> 01:22:50.490
他們都叫我巴茲
They call me Buzz.


1296
01:22:57.140 --> 01:22:59.070
是不是老鼠?
Was it a rat?


1297
01:22:59.170 --> 01:23:00.900
對  好大一隻
Yeah, a great big one.


1298
01:23:03.440 --> 01:23:05.270
拿去
Here.


1299
01:23:05.410 --> 01:23:07.280
洛杉磯警察局的一點心意
Compliments of the Police Department.


1300
01:23:24.400 --> 01:23:27.390
本周兇殺旅館最迷人的胃
Stomach of the week from a motel homicide.


1301
01:23:27.530 --> 01:23:31.250
這位失業的演員吃過熱狗  薯條  酒
Unemployed actor had frankfurter, French fries, alcohol and sperm.


1302
01:23:31.260 --> 01:23:34.120
還有精液  好豐盛的最後晚餐對不對?
Hell of a last supper, don't you think?


1303
01:23:34.130 --> 01:23:37.300
夜貓子那個案子你有沒有覺得不對勁?
Anything bothering you about the Nite Owl case?


1304
01:23:37.440 --> 01:23:39.570
有  就是你們一直纏著不放
That you guys won't let it get filed away.


1305
01:23:40.650 --> 01:23:41.700
這是什麼意思?
-What do you mean?


1306
01:23:41.850 --> 01:23:43.820
巴德·懷特他今天也來問過我
-Bud White grilled me on it today.


1307
01:23:45.280 --> 01:23:46.310
巴德·懷特?
Bud White?


1308
01:23:46.450 --> 01:23:49.640
他沒有我想的那麼笨
He's not as dumb as I thought.


1309
01:23:51.490 --> 01:23:54.020
他跟你說過話後  有沒有說跟你說過要去哪裏
Did he say where he was going after he talked to you?


1310
01:24:06.770 --> 01:24:08.570
讓我的女兒安息吧
Let my daughter rest in peace!


1311
01:24:08.710 --> 01:24:10.830
雷佛太太  我想問你一些問題
Mrs. Lefferts, I want to ask a few questions.


1312
01:24:10.980 --> 01:24:13.910
懷特警官已經去下面看過了
Officer White already checked under the house.


1313
01:24:14.050 --> 01:24:15.740
屋子下面?
Under the house?


1314
01:24:15.880 --> 01:24:17.820
那裏?  外面後頭
-Where? -Out back.


1315
01:24:19.620 --> 01:24:21.450
他只找到老鼠而已
All he found was rodents.


1316
01:24:24.690 --> 01:24:26.620
盡快幫我查明死者身份
I need an I.D. on this as soon as possible.


1317
01:24:26.730 --> 01:24:28.160
而且你只能向我報告
Talk only to me on this one.


1318
01:24:29.430 --> 01:24:31.400
影星首映場前吸毒被捕

1319
01:24:31.530 --> 01:24:33.090
文生  我有件事需要你幫忙
I need your help.


1320
01:24:33.100 --> 01:24:36.670
我現在很忙你為什麼不找你們兇殺組同仁
I'm busy right now. Why don't you ask your boys in Homicide?


1321
01:24:40.040 --> 01:24:43.440
不行  我需要兇殺組以外的人
I can't. I need someone outside of Homicide.


1322
01:24:43.540 --> 01:24:46.230
我要你跟蹤巴得懷特直到他今天晚上去值勤為止
Tail Bud White until he goes on duty this evening.


1323
01:24:47.680 --> 01:24:50.410
幫幫忙  離我遠一點吧
Do me a real favor and leave me alone.


1324
01:24:51.180 --> 01:24:53.210
你相信那三個黑人是夜貓子案的兇手嗎?
You make the Negroes for the Nite Owl killings?


1325
01:24:56.560 --> 01:24:57.750
什麼?
What?


1326
01:24:57.760 --> 01:24:59.720
這是很簡單的問題
It's a simple question.


1327
01:25:01.430 --> 01:25:06.930
你為什麼還要去追查夜貓子的案件呢?
Why in the world do you want to dig deeper into the Nite Owl killings


1328
01:25:06.940 --> 01:25:08.330
副組長
Lieutenant?


1329
01:25:11.700 --> 01:25:12.900
羅羅·湯馬西
Rollo Tomasi.


1330
01:25:15.270 --> 01:25:17.610
你還要給我其它提示還是要我開始猜了?
Is there more or do I have to guess?


1331
01:25:20.350 --> 01:25:23.010
羅羅是個扒手
Rollo was a purse snatcher.


1332
01:25:27.050 --> 01:25:28.680
先父有一次下了班後捉到他
My father ran into him off-duty.


1333
01:25:31.060 --> 01:25:34.620
他朝我父親開了六槍卻逃之夭夭
He shot my father 6 times and got away clean.


1334
01:25:35.590 --> 01:25:37.860
沒有人知道他真實的身份
No one knew who he was.


1335
01:25:38.300 --> 01:25:40.530
我為了讓這個人真實一點  所以給他取了這個名字
I made the name up to give him personality.


1336
01:25:42.300 --> 01:25:43.860
你到底想講什麼?
What's your point?


1337
01:25:44.000 --> 01:25:46.440
羅羅·湯馬西是我成為警察的原動力
Rollo Tomasi's the reason I became a cop.


1338
01:25:47.470 --> 01:25:48.300
我一心想要捉到
I wanted to catch the guys...


1339
01:25:48.440 --> 01:25:50.070
那些自以為可以逍遙法外的人
who thought they could get away with it.


1340
01:25:52.380 --> 01:25:54.640
我希望能夠尋得天道公理
It was supposed to be about justice.


1341
01:25:55.280 --> 01:25:57.910
可是慢慢的我失去了那份理想
Then somewhere along the way I lost sight of that.


1342
01:26:02.420 --> 01:26:03.820
你為什麼當警察?
Why'd you become a cop?


1343
01:26:14.330 --> 01:26:15.770
我不記得了
I don't remember.


1344
01:26:22.670 --> 01:26:24.610
你到底要什麼?  艾斯利
What do you want, Exley?


1345
01:26:24.710 --> 01:26:26.770
我希望能破了這個案子
I want to solve this thing.


1346
01:26:26.950 --> 01:26:29.110
夜貓子已經破了
Nite Owl was solved.


1347
01:26:29.250 --> 01:26:30.310
沒有
No.


1348
01:26:31.480 --> 01:26:33.380
我希望能夠真正的破案
I want to do it right.


1349
01:26:33.490 --> 01:26:36.220
即使是你必須付出慘痛代價
Even if it means paying the consequences?


1350
01:26:39.390 --> 01:26:41.690
好  大學生  我幫你
All right, college boy, I'll help.


1351
01:26:41.830 --> 01:26:44.390
不過有個案子  你們兇殺組根本不在乎
But there's a case your boys in Homicide don't care about.


1352
01:26:44.530 --> 01:26:48.230
他們認為只是稀鬆平常的命案
They think it's just another Hollywood "homo"-cide.


1353
01:26:48.240 --> 01:26:49.460
可是我不認為
But I don't.


1354
01:26:49.600 --> 01:26:51.090
你幫我查我的案子
You help me with mine,


1355
01:26:51.240 --> 01:26:53.170
我就幫你查你的案子
I'll help you with yours.


1356
01:26:53.270 --> 01:26:54.970
一言為定?
Deal?


1357
01:26:55.070 --> 01:26:56.340
一言為定
Deal.


1358
01:27:28.470 --> 01:27:30.100
強寧·史當巴那多
Johnny Stompanato.


1359
01:27:31.640 --> 01:27:33.980
溫德爾懷特警員  你好嗎? 老兄
