那還有誰會說出去呢
who's to say what happened?


1857
02:09:26.760 --> 02:09:29.460
或許史密斯是像英雄般殉職的
Maybe Dudley Smith died a hero.


1858
02:09:29.570 --> 02:09:32.360
好主意  如果媒體肯跟我們合作
-Good idea. -lf we get the press to play.


1859
02:09:39.980 --> 02:09:42.380
要不要告訴我你在笑什麼
Want to tell me what you're smiling about?


1860
02:09:48.120 --> 02:09:49.180
英雄
A hero.


1861
02:09:50.050 --> 02:09:51.780
他怎麼知道我們在說什麼
How'd he know what we said?


1862
02:09:52.060 --> 02:09:53.320
他不可能聽見的
He couldn't have heard us.


1863
02:09:57.290 --> 02:09:59.590
在這種情況下
In this situation


1864
02:09:59.700 --> 02:10:01.190
一個英雄是不夠的
you'll need more than one.


1865
02:10:07.040 --> 02:10:08.230
"警局組長英雄般殉職 "

1866
02:10:08.340 --> 02:10:11.430
本人深感榮幸能再一次
It is my pleasure to present this award to


1867
02:10:11.540 --> 02:10:16.210
頒發勇士勳章給埃德蒙艾斯利警官
Detective Lieutenant Edmund Exley two-time Medal of Valor recipient.


1868
02:10:26.260 --> 02:10:29.710
本局明年將遷至新大樓
Next year the LAPD will move into its new facility.


1869
02:10:30.760 --> 02:10:32.460
有了艾斯利這樣的楷模
With leaders like Edmund Exley


1870
02:10:32.560 --> 02:10:35.900
本局同仁貪污舞弊的惡劣形象  將一掃而空
the image of fat cops stealing apples will be left behind


1871
02:10:36.000 --> 02:10:39.460
洛杉磯也終於有了應有的警力
and Los Angeles will finally have the police force it deserves.


1872
02:10:53.750 --> 02:10:55.910
你就是受不了誘惑
You just couldn't resist.


1873
02:10:56.020 --> 02:10:58.390
他們要利用我嘛  我又何妨也利用利用他們
They're using me. So for a while, I'm using them.


1874
02:11:00.720 --> 02:11:01.750
出來一下
Come on.


1875
02:11:36.760 --> 02:11:37.920
謝謝你推了我一把
Thanks for the push.


1876
02:11:59.580 --> 02:12:01.240
恭喜你了  警官
Congratulations, Lieutenant Exley.


1877
02:12:05.090 --> 02:12:07.610
有人贏得了全世界
Some men get the world


1878
02:12:07.720 --> 02:12:10.960
有人則贏得了從良妓女  以及亞歷桑那之旅
others get ex-hookers and a trip to Arizona.